{"tid":1581903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「9，２１」一句講晒 元朗靜坐 會唔會叫口號","createTime":"2019-09-19T19:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T16:14:37.000Z","uid":13385,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c267e0bfaf672e53dc608297466e3a10f5a2ec5","tid":1581903,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次個元朗靜坐  <br />\n有啲人又話 叫口號 又啲又ｓｈｕｕｕｕ人叫人靜<br />\n叫口號既又話靜既　有潔癖　叫口號都唔得<br />\n靜既又話要表示　哀傷　尊重傷者　所以靜<br />\n兩邊差啲鬧交   割蓆咁濟<br />\n一句講晒 元朗靜坐 會唔會叫口號<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「靜」坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會叫口號<br />\n定 想叫就叫　想靜就靜 ！！"},{"pid":"cc882358c42e957348a0dc73d154170992ceb056","tid":1581903,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T20:02:46.000Z","msg":"上次靜撚同口號撚隔一陣就擦槍走火，跳哂制咁互鬧，根本無人尊重緊件事"},{"pid":"e02174ca7d6e2fb98c745fa7cef651d57dfb7a6a","tid":1581903,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc882358c42e957348a0dc73d154170992ceb056","tid":1581903,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T20:02:46.000Z","msg":"上次靜撚同口號撚隔一陣就擦槍走火，跳哂制咁互鬧，根本無人尊重緊件事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T20:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以咪要有個共識<br />\n做和事佬  兩邊又唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dede45cb5a0e9e2e440fd7ac02065920dc6b7ae6","tid":1581903,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T20:14:31.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）